plugins.rule_description.rule_page.0.lor: Breaking the rules will result in punishment!
plugins.rule_description.rule_page.1.lor:
Examples:
Using cheats, scripts, printers, or any unauthorized software to gain an unfair advantage.
plugins.rule_description.rule_page.2: Money laundering or multiple accounts are prohibited
plugins.rule_description.rule_page.2.lor:
Examples:
Abusing game mechanics or using alt accounts for exploits, or using multiple accounts to bypass limits.
plugins.rule_description.rule_page.3: Don't send obscene information, there are minors here
plugins.rule_description.rule_page.3.lor:
Examples:
Posting inappropriate, obscene, or pornographic content in any public channel (chat, signs, item names, etc.).
plugins.rule_description.rule_page.4: If it's not yours, leave it where it is
plugins.rule_description.rule_page.4.lor:
Examples:
Stealing from chests or farms; griefing or modifying builds without permission; interfering with redstone contraptions.
plugins.rule_description.rule_page.5: Take care of yourself and don't make others angry
plugins.rule_description.rule_page.5.lor:
Examples:
Unsolicited attacking or killing of players (outside PVP zones); harassment like trapping players or blocking their Nether Portals.
plugins.rule_description.rule_page.6: Respect, be friendly, and be inclusive to maintain a clean community
plugins.rule_description.rule_page.6.lor:
Examples:
Spamming, arguing, or using offensive language in public chat.
plugins.rule_description.rule_page.7: If you love to complain about this environment, then leave
plugins.rule_description.rule_page.7.lor: We welcome all positive members to the community and hope to maintain an enjoyable environment together.
